<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4">Welcome to the Kamal Demo</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Successfully deployed with Kamal!</p>
    <div class="mt-4 inline-block bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
      <% if ENV['KAMAL_DEPLOYED_AT'] %>
        <p>Deployed at: <%= ENV['KAMAL_DEPLOYED_AT'] %></p>
      <% else %>
        <p>Running in development mode</p>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">About Kamal</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Kamal is a deployment system for Ruby on Rails applications created by the team at Basecamp. It simplifies deploying Rails applications to one or multiple servers using Docker.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      With Kamal, you can easily:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
      <li>Build and push Docker images</li>
      <li>Deploy to multiple servers in parallel</li>
      <li>Roll back to previous versions if needed</li>
      <li>Set up SSL certificates automatically</li>
      <li>Monitor your application's health</li>
    </ul>
    <a href="https://github.com/basecamp/kamal" target="_blank" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded transition-colors">
      Check out Kamal on GitHub
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Server Information</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-2">Environment</h3>
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-3 rounded">
          <p><strong>Rails Env:</strong> <%= Rails.env %></p>
          <p><strong>Ruby Version:</strong> <%= RUBY_VERSION %></p>
          <p><strong>Rails Version:</strong> <%= Rails::VERSION::STRING %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-2">System</h3>
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-3 rounded">
          <p><strong>Hostname:</strong> <%= `hostname`.strip rescue "Unknown" %></p>
          <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= Time.now.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %H:%M:%S %Z") %></p>
          <p><strong>Load Avg:</strong> <%= `uptime | awk '{print $(NF-2)" "$(NF-1)" "$(NF)}'`.strip rescue "Unknown" %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-center">
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
      This is a simple demo page. Customize it to showcase your specific deployment features.
    </p>
    <div class="inline-flex space-x-4">
      <a href="https://kamal-deploy.org/docs/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Documentation</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/basecamp/kamal/discussions" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Community</a>
      <a href="https://world.hey.com/dhh/introducing-kamal-9330a267" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Introduction Post</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>